messages.message:
Just put up a PR (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/69465) to make three consistently failing cy tests non-blocking until they are fixed.
• `aihub-templates` and `build-project-crud`  failing due to a UI change that I’m working on the fix for
• `field-editor` seems to be failing because the model is returning `13 LIP 2006` instead of `13 LIP/JUL 2006` . @Udit have you ever seen this before here? do you think we should update the test to handle cases where the model output differs?\
Ah, that is annoying yah, easy fix would be to check for the new value format as well.
